gaza-building-killed-106-palestinians/0000018e-a9a8-dc75-afde-f9f869e30000</guid></item><item><title>起步晚，与右翼顾问会面：内塔尼亚胡加沙战争的第一个月</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-04/ty-article/.premium/late-starts-meetings-with-right-wing-advisers-netanyahus-first-month-of-the-gaza-war/0000018e-a975-d029-a78f-f9772a390000</link><description>他的日程细节证实了这位总理在加沙冲突初期的表现是多么糟糕。调查结果显示，即使在国家灾难和战争期间，内塔尼亚胡也会在早上相对较晚的时间去上班</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Apr 2024 15:27:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-04/ty-article/.premium/late-starts-meetings-with-right-wing-advisers-netanyahus-first-month-of-the-gaza-war/0000018e-a975-d029-a78f-f9772a390000</guid></item><item><title>以色列人和巴勒斯坦人被指控计划发动袭击、暗杀本格维尔</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-04/ty-article/.premium/israelis-palestinians-charged-with-plans-to-commit-attacks-assassinate-ben-gvir/0000018e-a982-d906-a5cf-ab9637fb0000</link><description>当局表示，这 10 名被起诉的嫌疑人还计划绑架士兵。在另一起案件中，另外三名以色列人因涉嫌策划袭击耶路撒冷体育场和警察局而被捕</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Apr 2024 15:13:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-04/ty-article/.premium/israelis-palestinians-charged-with-plans-to-commit-attacks-assassinate-ben-gvir/0000018e-a982-d906-a5cf-ab9637fb0000</guid></item><item><title>创纪录的 42 名以色列人登上福布斯 2024 年世界亿万富豪榜</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-04/ty-article/.premium/record-breaking-42-israelis-feature-on-forbes-world-billionaires-list-for-2024/0000018e-a973-dc69-ad9f-ebffe64c0000</link><description>福布斯榜单上的以色列人数量空前增加（其中包括赌场大亨谢尔登·阿德尔森的遗孀米里亚姆·阿德尔森），这可归因于以色列高科技产业的持续增长</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Apr 2024 14:45:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-04/ty-article/.premium/record-breaking-42-israelis-feature-on-forbes-world-billionaires-list-for-2024/0000018e-a973-dc69-ad9f-ebffe64c0000</guid></item><item><title>就像《黑道家族》中的情节一样：这位以色列人在正统暴徒中幸存下来后，将其拍成了电影</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/life/film/2024-04-04/ty-article-magazine/.premium/just-like-the-sopranos-after-surviving-a-haredi-mob-this-israeli-turned-it-into-a-film/0000018e-a3d3-d222-abef-a7fba4b80000</link><description>本尼·弗雷德曼在耶路撒冷极端正统社区之一开设一家电子产品商店差点丧命。在放弃正统派根源后，他拥抱了对电影的热爱，并带着他的震撼人心的新电影《家》回到了犯罪现场。</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Apr 2024 13:02:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/life/film/2024-04-04/ty-article-magazine/.premium/just-like-the-sopranos-after-surviving-a-haredi-mob-this-israeli-turned-it-into-a-film/0000018e-a3d3-d222-abef-a7fba4b80000</guid></item><item><title>我们以色列人必须立即采取行动，结束我们帮助造成的加沙人道主义危机</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-04-04/ty-article-opinion/.premium/we-israelis-must-act-now-to-end-the-humanitarian-crisis-in-gaza-we-helped-create/0000018e-a416-dd6b-abae-f757969e0000</link><description>加沙的公共卫生灾难对加沙人来说是一场生存危机。如果我们以色列人不开始更清楚地展示我们的人性，如果我们背叛我们自己的基本价值观，那对我们来说也将是灾难性的</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Apr 2024 12:55:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-04-04/ty-article-opinion/.premium/we-israelis-must-act-now-to-end-the-humanitarian-crisis-in-gaza-we-helped-create/0000018e-a416-dd6b-abae-f757969e0000</guid></item><item><title>34 岁的利多尔·利维 (Lidor Levy) 在以色列南部恐怖袭击中受伤身亡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-04/ty-article/.premium/lidor-levy-34-dies-of-wounds-sustained-in-terror-attack-in-southern-israel/0000018e-a8d1-d40c-adef-fff36d4d0000</link><description>利维是周日甘亚夫内购物中心持刀袭击事件中受伤的三人之一，留下了怀孕的妻子、六个月大的婴儿、父母和两个兄弟姐妹</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Apr 2024 11:42:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-04/ty-article/.premium/lidor-levy-34-dies-of-wounds-sustained-in-terror-attack-in-southern-israel/0000018e-a8d1-d40c-adef-fff36d4d0000</guid></item><item><title>土耳其航空将所有往返以色列的航班冻结期限延长至 2025 年 3 月</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-04/ty-article/.premium/turkish-airlines-extends-freeze-on-all-flights-to-and-from-israel-until-march-2025/0000018e-a8b2-d801-abce-adf743130000</link><description>国有土耳其航空公司将其特拉维夫航班暂停期延长六个月之际，正值以色列和土耳其之间的外交紧张局势加剧，并且即将迎来以色列最繁忙的旅行季节</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Apr 2024 11:33:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-04/ty-article/.premium/turkish-airlines-extends-freeze-on-all-flights-to-and-from-israel-until-march-2025/0000018e-a8b2-d801-abce-adf743130000</guid></item><item><title>以色列抗议者阻挡警察水枪：“我这样做是为了保护人质的家人”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-04/ty-article/.premium/israeli-protester-who-blocked-police-water-canon-i-did-it-to-protect-hostages-families/0000018e-a889-dfed-ad9f-aadbbb110000</link><description>阿隆·格罗佐夫在耶路撒冷总理内塔尼亚胡官邸外举行抗议活动时，爬到警察高压水枪下，获释后对《国土报》表示：“我想到人质遭到虐待，这就是我坚持下去的动力。”</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Apr 2024 11:26:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-04/ty-article/.premium/israeli-protester-who-blocked-police-water-canon-i-did-it-to-protect-hostages-families/0000018e-a889-dfed-ad9f-aadbbb110000</guid></item><item><title>“我们很遗憾来到这里”：耶路撒冷帐篷营地反内塔尼亚胡抗议的真正含义</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-04/ty-article-magazine/.premium/were-sad-to-be-here-what-the-jerusalem-tent-camp-anti-netanyahu-protest-really-was/0000018e-a486-dd6b-abae-f7c743c30000</link><description>为期四天的集中营呼吁关注加沙人质，在一个晚上与警方发生冲突期间成为头条新闻，但大多数时候，活动人士立即聚集在一起，询问如何不屈服于绝望</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Apr 2024 11:14:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-04/ty-article-magazine/.premium/were-sad-to-be-here-what-the-jerusalem-tent-camp-anti-netanyahu-protest-really-was/0000018e-a486-dd6b-abae-f7c743c30000</guid></item><item><title>即使在大马士革袭击之后，以色列-伊朗影子战争的游戏规则也没有改变</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-04/ty-article/.premium/rules-of-the-game-in-iranian-shadow-war-are-unchanged-even-after-israels-damascus-attack/0000018e-a840-dd6b-abae-ff431a9e0000</link><description>周一以色列直接袭击伊朗驻大马士革领事馆后，关键问题是伊朗是否会冒着失去与以色列直接对抗的“抵抗轴心”战略的风险，是否会开辟一条针对以色列的直接战线</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Apr 2024 11:05:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-04/ty-article/.premium/rules-of-the-game-in-iranian-shadow-war-are-unchanged-even-after-israels-damascus-attack/0000018e-a840-dd6b-abae-ff431a9e0000</guid></item><item><title>由于担心伊朗威胁，以色列将 GPS 干扰范围扩大到特拉维夫和耶路撒冷</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-04-04/ty-article/.premium/israel-extends-gps-jamming-to-tel-aviv-and-jerusalem-amid-fears-over-iranian-threats/0000018e-a7dd-dd6b-abae-f7dfc9f20000</link><description>由于担心伊朗对大马士革高级将军遇刺事件做出反应，以色列扩大了 GPS 干扰力度，导致以色列地图服务显示以色列人在贝鲁特和开罗的位置</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Apr 2024 10:17:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-04-04/ty-article/.premium/israel-extends-gps-jamming-to-tel-aviv-and-jerusalem-amid-fears-over-iranian-threats/0000018e-a7dd-dd6b-abae-f7dfc9f20000</guid></item><item><title>阿尔及利亚犹太钢琴家莫里斯·埃尔·梅迪奥尼的去世结束了一个音乐时代</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/life/2024-04-04/ty-article/.premium/death-of-algerian-jewish-pianist-maurice-el-medioni-ends-a-musical-era/0000018e-a82f-dd6b-abae-ff6fd5050000</link><description>这位音乐家于上个月去世，享年 95 岁，他将北非音乐与拉丁和非裔美国音乐结合在一起。他在晚年才成名，但在以色列为获得认可而奋斗</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Apr 2024 09:49:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/life/2024-04-04/ty-article/.premium/death-of-algerian-jewish-pianist-maurice-el-medioni-ends-a-musical-era/0000018e-a82f-dd6b-abae-ff6fd5050000</guid></item><item><title>财政部发现，目前现役以色列预备役军人数量是预算的两倍</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-04/ty-article/.premium/number-of-active-israeli-reservists-currently-double-what-was-budgeted-for-treasury-finds/0000018e-9f75-d6b5-a39f-bf7da0510000</link><description>数千名原本在义务服役后被释放的以色列义务兵在 10 月 7 日之后立即转为预备役军人，并获得了加薪。 IDF：数字比预测高出近 30-40%</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Apr 2024 07:49:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-04/ty-article/.premium/number-of-active-israeli-reservists-currently-double-what-was-budgeted-for-treasury-finds/0000018e-9f75-d6b5-a39f-bf7da0510000</guid></item><item><title>以色列人权组织向高等法院请愿，迫使政府增加对加沙的援助</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-04/ty-article/.premium/israeli-human-rights-groups-petition-high-court-to-force-government-to-increase-gaza-aid/0000018e-a41d-d40c-adef-f7ff95e30000</link><description>请愿书由四个人权组织提交，呼吁以色列当局允许所有援助物资、设备和人道主义人员自由、快速和不受阻碍地通行，特别是前往加沙地带北部。政府否认了所有针对它的指控</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Apr 2024 03:00:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-04/ty-article/.premium/israeli-human-rights-groups-petition-high-court-to-force-government-to-increase-gaza-aid/0000018e-a41d-d40c-adef-f7ff95e30000</guid></item><item><title>以色列处于高度戒备状态，担心伊朗会对大马士革的杀戮进行报复</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-04/ty-article/.premium/israel-on-high-alert-amid-fears-iran-will-seek-revenge-for-damascus-killings/0000018e-a595-dfed-ad9f-afdfedbd0000</link><description>所有迹象都表明，德黑兰决心对以色列暗杀叙利亚革命卫队高级指挥官的指控做出回应，而以色列国防军已经加强了防空司令部，以应对可能来自伊斯兰共和国的导弹或无人机袭击。加沙的车队是一个更广泛现象的征兆：当平民在附近时，士兵们就会开枪。</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Apr 2024 03:00:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-04/ty-article/.premium/israel-on-high-alert-amid-fears-iran-will-seek-revenge-for-damascus-killings/0000018e-a595-dfed-ad9f-afdfedbd0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列被拘留加沙人野战医院的医生：“我们都是违法行为的同谋”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-04/ty-article/.premium/doctor-at-idf-field-hospital-for-detained-gazans-we-are-all-complicit-in-breaking-law/0000018e-a59c-dfed-ad9f-afdfb5ce0000</link><description>以色列监狱设施的一名医生说，“两名囚犯因手铐受伤而被截肢”，他在给部长、总检察长的信中描述了恶劣的条件以及违反医疗道德和法律的行为</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Apr 2024 03:00:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-04/ty-article/.premium/doctor-at-idf-field-hospital-for-detained-gazans-we-are-all-complicit-in-breaking-law/0000018e-a59c-dfed-ad9f-afdfb5ce0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军情报负责人警告“复杂的日子”；火箭击中以色列北部房屋</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-04/ty-article-live/idf-says-it-will-draft-more-reservists-into-air-defense-command-amid-iran-threats/0000018e-a6d1-dfed-ad9f-aedbfc6c0000</link><description>以色列国防军表示，将在伊朗威胁下征召更多预备役人员加入防空司令部 ■ 周日恐怖袭击中受伤的男子伤重不治 ■ 美国国防部长劳埃德·奥斯汀对援助人员的死亡“感到愤怒” ■ 11 人因涉嫌策划刺杀部长伊塔马尔·本而被捕-Gvir ■ 哈马斯领导人哈尼亚表示，如果以色列国防军不从加沙撤军，就不会达成协议，“光荣的囚犯交换”</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Apr 2024 02:03:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-04/ty-article-live/idf-says-it-will-draft-more-reservists-into-air-defense-command-amid-iran-threats/0000018e-a6d1-dfed-ad9f-aedbfc6c0000</guid></item></channel></rss>